				<p>These are definitely good as a king of cookie (i made the thinner top), but not my holy grail lemon bar. I do like a little bit more give, not quite such a rock solid base, and too much flour in the lemon top. I&#8217;m going to try some of those suggested here next time. The CI recipe with cream looks like it&#8217;s on the right track since a curd typically has butter in it. Good recipe for my first attempt at a lemon bar though. Thanks Deb!</p>
